All Implemented Interfaces:
StackList<NodeType,EdgeType>, Strategy<NodeType,EdgeType>, Generic<NodeType,EdgeType>, java.lang.Iterable<MiningStack<NodeType,EdgeType>>, java.util.Collection<MiningStack<NodeType,EdgeType>>
public class ThreadedDFSStrategy<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends ListItem<MiningStack<NodeType,EdgeType>>
implements Strategy<NodeType,EdgeType>, StackList<NodeType,EdgeType>

This class represents the threaded DFS search It is also the head-element of the double linked MiningStack (ring) list and therefore responsible for the work distribution

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
